{
  "page": "Desmond Grell",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Grell\" title=\"House Grell\"><img alt=\"House Grell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/af/House_Grell.svg/50px-House_Grell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/af/House_Grell.svg/75px-House_Grell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/af/House_Grell.svg/100px-House_Grell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Desmond Grell</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Grell\" title=\"House Grell\"><img alt=\"House Grell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/af/House_Grell.svg/50px-House_Grell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/af/House_Grell.svg/75px-House_Grell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/af/House_Grell.svg/100px-House_Grell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Jeff_Lee_Johnson_Ser_Desmond_Grell.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Jeff Lee Johnson Ser Desmond Grell.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d2/Jeff_Lee_Johnson_Ser_Desmond_Grell.png/350px-Jeff_Lee_Johnson_Ser_Desmond_Grell.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d2/Jeff_Lee_Johnson_Ser_Desmond_Grell.png/525px-Jeff_Lee_Johnson_Ser_Desmond_Grell.png 1.5x, /images/d/d2/Jeff_Lee_Johnson_Ser_Desmond_Grell.png 2x\" /></a><div>Desmond by Lee Johnson © Fantasy Flight Games</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Master-at-arms\" title=\"Master-at-arms\">Master-at-arms</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">Castellan</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Grell\" title=\"House Grell\">House Grell</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_238_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">238</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_240_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">240&#160;AC</a> (roughly)<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Desmond Grell</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Grell\" title=\"House Grell\">House Grell</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Master-at-arms\" title=\"Master-at-arms\">master-at-arms</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> He has spent the better part of his life in service to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">House Tully</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Desmond\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Desmond</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Desmond_Grell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>An old <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Desmond is stout with a large belly.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Courteous<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and brave,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> he enjoys <a href=\"/index.php/Alcohol\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Alcohol\">alcohol</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> and bawdy jokes.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Desmond_Grell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Desmond was born of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Grell\" title=\"House Grell\">House Grell</a>, one of the minor houses of the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>. He entered the service of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster Tully</a> at a young age. He was a squire when Hoster's daughter <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn</a> was born, a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> by the time she learned to ride, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Master-at-arms\" title=\"Master-at-arms\">master-at-arms</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> before she was wed to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> During Catelyn's <a href=\"/index.php/Bedding\" title=\"Bedding\">bedding</a> on <a href=\"/index.php/Weddings_of_Catelyn_and_Lysa_Tully\" title=\"Weddings of Catelyn and Lysa Tully\">her wedding night</a>, Desmond drunkenly apologized for each bawdy joke he made.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Desmond_Grell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Desmond_Grell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Desmond trains new bowmen after the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Camps\" title=\"Battle of the Camps\">Battle of the Camps</a> and the proclamation of <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">King in the North</a>. Instead of accompanying <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a> to see their father, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster Tully</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a> goes to speak with the bowmen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During <a href=\"/index.php/Plot_to_free_Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Plot to free Jaime Lannister\">the attempt</a> to free Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> from his cell at <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a>, Desmond's squire <a href=\"/index.php/Myles_(squire)\" title=\"Myles (squire)\">Myles</a> is slain by Jaime.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Desmond is introduced to <a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_Tarth\" title=\"Brienne Tarth\">Brienne Tarth</a> when she and Catelyn return from <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End_(299)\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End (299)\">Storm's End</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When Edmure rides out to meet the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> forces at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Fords\" title=\"Battle of the Fords\">Battle of the Fords</a>, he leaves Desmond as commander of Riverrun's meager garrison in his absence. Desmond provides updates about the fighting to Catelyn.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Desmond drunkenly sings along when <a href=\"/index.php/Rymund_the_Rhymer\" title=\"Rymund the Rhymer\">Rymund the Rhymer</a> performs \"<a href=\"/index.php/Wolf_in_the_Night\" title=\"Wolf in the Night\">Wolf in the Night</a>\" in the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Hall_of_Riverrun\" title=\"Great Hall of Riverrun\">Great Hall of Riverrun</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> The <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> is elated when Edmure sends word of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>'s retreat from the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Fork\" title=\"Red Fork\">Red Fork</a>, and he has some casks opened to celebrate Edmure's victory at <a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Mill\" title=\"Stone Mill\">Stone Mill</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Desmond later has twenty casks of nut-brown <a href=\"/index.php/Ale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ale\">ale</a> brought up from the cellar so that the <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a> within Riverrun can celebrate Edmure's imminent return and the <a href=\"/index.php/Storming_of_the_Crag\" title=\"Storming of the Crag\">storming of the Crag</a> by King Robb, Catelyn's son.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Desmond_Grell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Desmond was named <a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">castellan</a> of Riverrun when Edmure departed to defend the fords of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Fork\" title=\"Red Fork\">Red Fork</a>. After Catelyn releases Jaime Lannister from the dungeon without permission, <a href=\"/index.php/Utherydes_Wayn\" title=\"Utherydes Wayn\">Utherydes Wayn</a> and a red-faced Desmond reluctantly address her treason. Desmond agrees with Catelyn's suggestion to be confined in her father Hoster's chambers while awaiting the return of her brother Edmure and son Robb.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Desmond sends Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Robin_Ryger\" title=\"Robin Ryger\">Robin Ryger</a> in pursuit of Jaime, Brienne, and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Cleos_Frey\" title=\"Cleos Frey\">Cleos Frey</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> but Robin and his men are forced to retreat after their river galley is destroyed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Desmond escorts Catelyn to the Great Hall when Robb returns from the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Desmond is to be one of the nobles who launch Lord Hoster's funeral boat after his passing. When <a href=\"/index.php/Lothar_Frey\" title=\"Lothar Frey\">Lothar Frey</a>, the envoy from the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a>, arrives with Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a>'s response to Robb's overtures, however, Robb quietly asks Desmond to step aside so that Lothar can participate in the ceremony.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Desmond_Grell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After Jaime achieves the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Riverrun\" title=\"Siege of Riverrun\">surrender of Riverrun</a>, Desmond and Robin ask to join the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>. Both are to be escorted to <a href=\"/index.php/Maidenpool\" title=\"Maidenpool\">Maidenpool</a> by a dozen of the <a href=\"/index.php/Mountain%27s_men\" title=\"Mountain&#39;s men\">Mountain's men</a> under the command of <a href=\"/index.php/Rafford\" title=\"Rafford\">Raff the Sweetling</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Desmond_Grell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Desmond</b>: Would that Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster</a> could have seen that. It would have made him dance.<br />\n</p><p><b>Catelyn</b>: My father's dancing days are past, I fear, and <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Fords\" title=\"Battle of the Fords\">this fight</a> is just begun. The <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannisters</a> will come again. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin</a> has twice my brother's numbers.<br />\n<b>Desmond</b>: He could have ten times and it would not matter. The west bank of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Fork\" title=\"Red Fork\">Red Fork</a> is higher than the east, my lady, and well wooded. Our bowmen have good cover, and a clear field for their shafts ... and should any breach occur, <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure</a> will have his best <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> in reserve, ready to ride wherever they are most sorely needed. The river will hold them.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Catelyn</b>: I pray that you are right.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Desmond and <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Desmond</b>: Oh, if only I might have been with him. Where is that fool <a href=\"/index.php/Rymund_the_Rhymer\" title=\"Rymund the Rhymer\">Rymund</a>? There's a song in this, by <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">the gods</a>, and one that even <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure</a> will want to hear. <a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Mill\" title=\"Stone Mill\">The mill</a> that ground the <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Mountain</a> down, I could almost make the words myself, had I the singer's gift.<br />\n<b>Catelyn</b>: I'll hear no songs until <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Fords\" title=\"Battle of the Fords\">the fighting's</a> done.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Desmond and <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Desmond</b>: Your sons. Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Vyman\" title=\"Vyman\">Vyman</a> told us. <a href=\"/index.php/Capture_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Capture of Winterfell\">The poor lads</a>. Terrible. Terrible. But ...<br />\n</p><p><b>Utherydes</b>: We share your grief, my lady. All <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> mourns with you, but ...<br />\n<b>Desmond</b>: The news must have driven you mad, a madness of grief, a mother's madness, men will understand. You did not know ...<br />\n</p>\n<b>Catelyn</b>: I did. I understood what I was doing and knew it was treasonous. If you fail to punish me, men will believe that we connived together to free <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a>. It was mine own act and mine alone, and I alone must answer for it.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Desmond, <a href=\"/index.php/Utherydes_Wayn\" title=\"Utherydes Wayn\">Utherydes Wayn</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">This castle's</a> been my home for forty years. You say I'm free to go, but where? I'm too old and too stout to make a <a href=\"/index.php/Hedge_knight\" title=\"Hedge knight\">hedge knight</a>. But men are always welcome at the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Desmond to <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Desmond\">Quotes about Desmond</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Desmond_Grell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Desmond\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Ser Desmond Grell had served <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">House Tully</a> all his life. He had been a squire when Catelyn was born, a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> when she learned to walk and ride and swim, <a href=\"/index.php/Master-at-arms\" title=\"Master-at-arms\">master-at-arms</a> by the day that she was wed. He had seen Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster's</a> little Cat become a young woman, <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">a great lord's</a> lady, mother to <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">a king</a>. And now he has seen me <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_1\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 1\">become a traitor</a> as well.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Desmond_Grell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages#Desmond_Grell\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages\">Desmond Grell</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Appendix\" ti